headline: Wall Street Breakfast Podcast: Palantir's Big Gains, Bigger Drop
summary: Palantir stock tumbles despite Q3 beat as analysts mull valuation. Denny's to be taken private in a $620 million deal. Starbucks offloads majority stake in China business to Boyu Capital.
